OOC: This one caught me a little by surprise. Perhaps I have missed a
post or two, but I thought Remus was still back at Maximal HQ? I am not
saying he cannot be here, but I just want to be sure I know what
happened so I can post the proper responses for the sweeps and such he
flew through, from the looks of it without stopping. I would think he
would have to be moving quite fast to know what Rodimus and Cyclonus
where up to and be able to react with the speed that he did. Remember
Cyclonus has only come to the water front last post - perhaps in the
last minute or so. Before that Cyclonus was in combat with Ravenchief,
moving swiftly across the city. Again I am just trying to be sure of
the details before I post a response.

Thanks

Preston
(Da'minion)
